								class Attribute1
								{
									property="ModuleCreateDiaryRecord_F_Title";
									expression="_this setVariable ['Title',_value,true];";
									class Value
									{
										class data
										{
											singleType="STRING";
											value="Background";
										};
									};
								};
								class Attribute2
								{
									property="ModuleCreateDiaryRecord_F_Description";
									expression="_this setVariable ['Description',_value,true];";
									class Value
									{
										class data
										{
											singleType="STRING";
											value="<font face='PuristaBold' color='#ff0000' size='15'>BACKGROUND</font>      " \n "<br/>  " \n "Chernarus, 2015 " \n "<br/><br/>   " \n "Post Operation 'Harvest Red', U.S. Troops are stationed in Chernarus to help stabilize the country, train CDF forces, and help hunt down the last remnants of the ChDKZ. " \n "<br/><br/>   " \n "Meanwhile, under the pretext of a ‘training exercise’, the Russian Federation began amassing large battlegroups near Chernarus. " \n "<br/><br/>   " \n "Russia then crossed into Chernarus with the goal of 'restoring order', in support of the ChDKZ and declaring the CDF government illegitimate. Starting a major escalation to an already bloody civil war. " \n "<br/><br/>   " \n "Striking from Takistan, the Green Sea and the Russian border. Quickly overwhelming CDF and U.S. positions. " \n "<br/><br/>   " \n "International condemnation of the invasion followed. " \n "<br/><br/>   " \n "The U.S. contingent were caught in the middle of an invasion. Outnumbered and cut off, desperately holding key terrain to buy time for the CDF to reorganize. " \n "<br/><br/>   " \n "The UN Security Council denounced the attack and recommended member states to repel the 'illegal' invasion. " \n "<br/><br/>  " \n "The U.S. will be the first to step in. Redeploying the 27th MEU back into Chernarus as well as the 15th MEU to support.";
										};
									};
								};
								class Attribute3
								{
									property="ModuleCreateDiaryRecord_F_Owner";
									expression="_this setVariable ['Owner',_value,true];";
									class Value
									{
										class data
										{
											singleType="SCALAR";
											value=3;
										};
									};
								};
								class Attribute4
								{
									property="ModuleCreateDiaryRecord_F_Subject";
									expression="_this setVariable ['Subject',_value,true];";
									class Value
									{
										class data
										{
											singleType="STRING";
											value="";
										};
									};
								};
								nAttributes=5;
							};
						};
						class Item10
						{
							dataType="Logic";
							class PositionInfo
							{
								position[]={2492.6079,122.19116,3145.583};
								angles[]={6.0426092,0,0.074525557};
							};
							id=1658;
							type="ModuleCreateDiaryRecord_F";
							atlOffset=-7.6293945e-06;
							class CustomAttributes
							{
								class Attribute0
								{
									property="ModuleCreateDiaryRecord_F_PresetTitle";
									expression="_this setVariable ['PresetTitle',_value,true];";
									class Value
									{
										class data
										{
											singleType="STRING";
											value="Situation";
										};
									};
								};
								class Attribute1
								{
									property="ModuleCreateDiaryRecord_F_Title";
									expression="_this setVariable ['Title',_value,true];";
									class Value
									{
										class data
										{
											singleType="STRING";
											value="Briefing";
										};
									};
								};
								class Attribute2
								{
									property="ModuleCreateDiaryRecord_F_Description";
									expression="_this setVariable ['Description',_value,true];";
									class Value
									{
										class data
										{
											singleType="STRING";
											value="<font face='PuristaBold' color='#fce300' size='15'>SITUATION</font>        " \n "<br/>     " \n "The MAGTF is due to arrive tomorrow, however the ChDKZ and the Russians are pushing us back hard. They started a new offensive in the southwest aiming to capture Zelenogorsk.  " \n "<br/><br/>     " \n "The ChDKZ were able to seize control of a strategic <marker name='marker_36'>hydroelectric dam</marker>. ISR was able to confirm the presence of two heavy artillery guns positioned on the ground behind the dam, before being shot down.  " \n "<br/><br/>     " \n "Those guns are currently being used to shell <marker name='marker_21'>friendly positions within Zelenogorsk</marker>. VDV elements have reinforced the area, making it difficult to get close.     " \n "<br/><br/>  " \n "With all elements in the south tied up with the defense, 1st Recon's the only one that can stop the guns. " \n "<br/><br/>    " \n "<font face='PuristaBold' color='#fce300' size='15'>ENEMY</font>        " \n "<br/>     " \n "ChDKZ insurgents maintain control of this AO. Expect light to moderate infantry patrols, static defenses, and checkpoints guarding key crossroads.  " \n "<br/><br/>     " \n "Russian VDV units are present in the AO aswell and will act as a Quick Reaction Force. They are well-trained, better equipped, and capable of rapid deployment once contact is made.  " \n "<br/><br/>     " \n "Enemy forces are expected to respond aggressively once they notice something wrong at the dam.  " \n "<br/><br/>     " \n "<font face='PuristaBold' color='#fce300' size='15'>MISSION</font>        " \n "<br/>     " \n "1st Recon will <marker name='marker_6'>infiltrate from the south</marker>, making your way up north towards the <marker name='marker_36'>Tishina Dam</marker>.  " \n "<br/><br/>     " \n "<marker name='marker_33'>Avoid the areas marked red in your map as that's where most enemies are currently concentrated on the offensive.</marker>  " \n "<br/><br/>     " \n "You can choose to either go from the <marker name='starrail'>railway</marker> or the <marker name='dirt'>dirt path</marker>. Whatever choice it may be, you must <marker name='marker_0'>locate and destroy both artillery guns</marker> at the dam.  " \n "<br/><br/>     " \n "<marker name=''>Additionally, capture or eliminate the VDV HVT operating within the AO</marker>.  " \n "<br/><br/>     " \n "Once your objectives are complete, exfiltrate immediately before enemy reinforcements overwhelm your position.";
										};
									};
								};
								class Attribute3
